  "body": "<h2>Summary</h2>\nMy original resource pack, <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/skns-topsy-textures\">SKN's Topsy Fixes</a>, now packaged and colored to fit into the <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/bare-bones\">Bare Bones</a> resource pack. This is actually the easiest pack, since I already had the model data set from my original resource pack.\n\n<h2>Images</h2>\n<h3>Side-by-Side Comparison</h3>\n<p>Before and after, respectively</p>\n\n  <img width=\"49.5%\" alt=\"if image has not loaded, please see the gallery.\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SjYqHnjE/images/13cf0ed8ee4f08dc3c2dea9da40c5a1004813e3c.png\">\n  <img width=\"49.5%\" alt=\"if image has not loaded, please see the gallery.\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SjYqHnjE/images/19685c8e600cb01220ee48879dc661ded7573719.png\">\n\n  <img width=\"49.5%\" alt=\"if image has not loaded, please see the gallery.\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SjYqHnjE/images/e51edd357624612cdd3ed92dd5aac6ce722aa169.png\">\n  <img width=\"49.5%\" alt=\"if image has not loaded, please see the gallery.\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SjYqHnjE/images/1458d4739ab495e0830cb02e7dc573b30f9c6f3e.png\">\n\n  <img width=\"49.5%\" alt=\"if image has not loaded, please see the gallery.\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SjYqHnjE/images/eba88a0b6a0896ad3cdc9de54cfb9eb8da2ee057.png\">\n  <img width=\"49.5%\" alt=\"if image has not loaded, please see the gallery.\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SjYqHnjE/images/ec28906ce3a2093252bb4b569e14b59a5efaf7e6.png\">\n\n<h3>Ingame Screenshots</h3>\n\n<img alt=\"if image has not loaded, please see the gallery.\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SjYqHnjE/images/1be9a661124cbd6a61384b20cabface91d5cbc96.png\">\n<img alt=\"if image has not loaded, please see the gallery.\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SjYqHnjE/images/722ae0797b796d46ca0ba228e298aba595b0ecd8.png\">\n\n<hr>\n<p>If you have any questions, comments, or ideas, please check out the wiki link and post them there.</p>",
